			<h2>Correspondence</h2>
			<a class="xsmall link-alt" href="https://www.thesunmagazine.org/letter-to-the-editor">Write a Letter to the Editor&nbsp;&#9656;</a>
		</div>

		<div id="article-correspondences" class="correspondences correspondences-collapsed">
								<div class="block-correspondence" id="2093">
		<blockquote class="quote-2">
			<p>I just finished rereading Sybil Smith&rsquo;s &ldquo;<a href="/article/542">Bible Hockey</a>&rdquo; [July 2003]. I can&rsquo;t remember when I&rsquo;ve been so moved by a memoir. She knows herself and has insight into the people around her (almost more than she can stand, I think). And she can write: every word counts.</p>

<p>I don&rsquo;t know whether Smith will ever find the kind of bliss-inducing God she&rsquo;s looking for, but if she continues to write, her readers will be blessed.</p>
							<p class="quote-2-author">Don MacQueen<br>Santa Rosa, California</p>
					</blockquote>
	</div>

